dwelling, residence, habitation;
{#harzo harzo hfdayavasatiH paMcabARastu bARaH#} 

<ls>P. R. 1. 22</ls>; <ls>Ś. 2. 14.</ls>

{@--3@} A 
receptacle, reservoir, an abode (<ab>fig.</ab>);
{#alakAmativAhyEva vasatiM vasusaMpadAM#}  
<ls>Ku. 6. 37</ls>; so {#vinayavasatiH, DarmEkavasatiH#}.

{@--5@} The time when one halts or
stays to rest, {%<ab>i. e.</ab>%} night; {#tasya#} 
{#mArgavaSAdekA baBUva vasatiryataH#} <ls>R. 15. 11</ls>
